reviewText: the instructor is wearing black on a black background and makes it very hard to follow

This DVD is so awesome! I can not work out to hard due to a diagnosis I received ,so I only do the first half and working toward the second. It's peaceful and calming I get to listen to awesome affirmation as I do this workout. Being a believe and being diagnosed with something that changes your life, these affirmations really boost my.spirt! So glad I got this!
this tape is challenging and fun, i love it
